
Setting up NQC on a modern machine:
-----------------------------------

1) Compile my edited version to use the kernel drivers!
2) chmod 777 /dev/lego0 and /dev/legousbtower0
3) You might, if I remember, have to symlink /dev/legousb or /dev/legousbtower, perhaps.
4) Flash firmware to the RCX (provided)
5) make!
